**1.2 Data Flow --- End to End**

The canonical CFI data flow as of March 2026:

12. Sharon uploads file (PDF / Excel / Word / lab result) to Claude
    Project chat

13. Claude reads file using active persona stack (Guardrails \>
    Anti-Hallucination \> Research \> Persona \> Process Engineer)

14. Claude writes SQL INSERT / UPDATE / CREATE TABLE statements

15. Sharon copies SQL → opens Supabase SQL Editor → New Query tab →
    pastes → runs

16. Lovable React app reads live data from Supabase via
    \@supabase/supabase-js direct client

17. Dashboard auto-updates via Supabase Realtime subscriptions

18. All CLASS A values remain locked --- no UI or SQL can overwrite them

